Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:06.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.71,0:00:09.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:17.09,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:26.53,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:29.96,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:41.72,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:48.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:53.06,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:55.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.41,0:01:03.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:12.62,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:16.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:21.76,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:27.97,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:35.02,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:39.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.61,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:45.99,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:48.95,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:52.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:53.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.25,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.27,0:01:58.96,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:01.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:05.76,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:08.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.47,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:14.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:18.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:21.27,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:25.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.51,0:02:33.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy \Nwhose body turned to rubber
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:03:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.47,0:03:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat crew landed \Non the Sabaody Archipelago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to search for a ship coating craftsman \Nto help them reach Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During the adventure, Camie, a mermaid \Nwho was with them, was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After determining her location,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami and company attempted \Nto win her in an auction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way from Fish-Man \NIsland, the mermaid Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're selling Camie now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We're gonna get her \Nback! We have 200 million here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Nami's plan failed \Nin an unforeseen manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy it for 500 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So suddenly?! We don't have that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let this happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let our friend get \Nbought and taken away like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie! We've been looking \Neverywhere! What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Straw Hat! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi tried to hold Luffy back as \Nhe went to rescue Camie, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a fish-man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi was then gunned down \Nby a Celestial Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't... Don't be mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised not to defy \Nthe Celestial Dragons,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if you saw someone get shot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lousy fish, still blabbering \Non even though I shot you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You annoy me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:05:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look, you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys'll get in huge trouble too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-ya...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You annoy me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Major Panic! Desperate \NStruggle at the Auction House"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saint Charloss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Charloss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:06:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punching this guy means a navy admiral \Nis gonna come here with a warship...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I missed my chance to cut him down \Nbecause you beat him up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi! Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.62,0:07:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all in big trouble now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't help it! That's just how Luffy is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess that makes it clear \Nwhat we gotta do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the key to Camie's collar \Nis probably somewhere backstage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to tend to Hachi's \Ninjury! You get the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charloss...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Charloss! Not even \NFather has ever struck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you, a commoner, \Nlay a hand on my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.50,0:07:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They've made the Celestial Dragons mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Get outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave! Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit pushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you what happens \Nwhen you assault us,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the descendants of this world's Creators!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if we care, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you strike Saint Roswald!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.73,0:08:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joue!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.94,0:08:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Concasser!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Franky! Free Camie-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.67,0:08:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Super leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guards! Get them! Seize the pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They just keep coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a ruckus. Sounds like \Nsomething's happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a fool would protect a lousy fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Maki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strong Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...And Fresh Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way, outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you all...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out for thunderclouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:10:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunderbolt Tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You intend to defy us to \Nthe very end, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Battle-Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie isn't for sale!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Call for a navy admiral and a warship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.89,0:10:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let them see who's boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When are we gonna get there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:11:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon! We're in Grove #1 now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, the busty girl, the \Nyoung master, the swordsman,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the panties guy, and the \Nreindeer have already arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That means the only ones \Nwho are late are Robin, Brook...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! How could this happen \Nto the great Usopp-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit thrashing around! That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a beautiful sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, I owe you one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know better than to jump off early!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who shook me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were going too fast. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be going on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate struck a Celestial Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:12:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy Headquarters is going \Nto send a warship now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:10.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this! I should have \Njust paid for my slave and left!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.88,0:12:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a waste to \Nuse that to buy someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll use it in a \Nmore productive way instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure! I'm gonna wear \Ndown my heels at this rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.72,0:12:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,36 Pound Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.02,0:13:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?! They didn't do \Nanything bad to you, did they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine! But you've been hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! Who do you take me for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Hachi, the takoyaki seller!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang on a little \Nlonger! Wait right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Hatchin! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the rumors said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.33,0:13:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He's one crazy bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat-ya Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A 300 million Berry bounty, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An uproar is already underway. There's \Na flood of people at the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only choice is to jump into the \Nfray! Just crash into it, if you would!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.87,0:14:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! I-I need to prepare myself first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My "can't go to auction houses" disease...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More flying fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.89,0:14:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cien Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just cracked my back...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right! Milk heals \Nme since I'm nothing but bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:15:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nothing but bones \Nand bones! Viva calcium!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then! Pardon my late entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clutch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Guard the mermaid at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,500 million! She sold for 500 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exterminate them at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, folks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to fear now \Nthat Usopp-sama is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hero is always the \Nlast to make an entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the headliner here, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.98,0:15:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So high up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm here, maybe I'll \Njust fret for a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get going already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.26,0:15:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually would've preferred \Nto do it at my own pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll punish these cretins by \Nstuffing and preserving the women
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and making the men slaves and starving them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww, oww...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that didn't hurt that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saint Roswald, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just repeated your crime, pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.40,0:16:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Robin! Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like everyone's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Where's Camie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there! We'll run away as soon \Nas the bomb around her neck is off!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry before the \Nwarship and admiral get here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.85,0:16:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The navy's already here, Straw Hat-ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that bear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've had the place surrounded \Nbefore the auctions even began.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy Headquarters has a post \Non this archipelago, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave the area immediately! \NIt's all right! We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it look inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've finished evacuating the patrons!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.36,0:17:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three Celestial Dragons are still inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring them out at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn pirates! Don't think \Nyou'll get out of here unhurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno who they wanted to catch,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I doubt they expected anyone \Nwould beat up the Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an interesting show \Nyou gave, Straw Hat-ya crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Trafalgar Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy. He's a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! The bear, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the man over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eustass Captain Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! That's the one with a \Nhigher bounty than Luffy-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:17:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, I'll kill this \Nmermaid that they're after!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 500 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-Please wait, Saint Shalria!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That item hasn't been paid for yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait, Saint Shalria! Saint Shalria!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, commoner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, fish! This is \Nthe end, once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Camie-chan's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.05,0:18:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your squirming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! We can't stop her in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saint Shalria!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, Mr. Giant?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place is in a real uproar. \NI'd say the auction's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've stolen some money now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so guess I'll head back \Nto the gambling houses...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one disagreeable old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were only here to get some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping for a chance to steal \Nfrom whoever bought me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess it wasn't meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. I'm all out. \NFirst thing is more alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about you, but I wouldn't \Nwant an old man like me for a slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Looks like we've \Ngarnered some attention...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that old man and that giant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are today's merchandise! How \Ndid they get out of their cell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.21,0:20:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have collars! \NHow did they unlock them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:21:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? Catching people is \Noutside of our field of expertise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't hold back an unshackled giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Rayleigh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Rayleigh, the coating craftsman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Is that you, Hachi?! It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.07,0:21:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to see you again! \NWhat are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get that injury?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay, you needn't say a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.53,0:22:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short... I see. I understand \Nthe situation now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure got yourself into \Na heap of trouble, Hachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.69,0:22:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you folks saved him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.75,0:22:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.30,0:22:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! How?! What did you just do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.66,0:22:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this old guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.58,0:22:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That straw hat suits dauntless men very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been wanting to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.42,0:23:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always causing problems, \None after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Given that World Nobles are the victims \Nhere, we will need to take action, Sengoku-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kizaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.77,0:23:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.15,0:23:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Admiral Kizaru Takes Action! \NSabaody Archipelago Thrown into Chaos"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
